Package com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.relocation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JarRelocator
    Relocates classes and resources within a jar file.
    JarRelocatorTask
    A task that copies jar entries from a jar input to a jar output, applying the relocations defined by a RelocatingRemapper.
    RelocatingClassVisitor
    A ClassVisitor that relocates types and names with a RelocatingRemapper.
    RelocatingRemapper
    Remaps class names and types using defined Relocation rules.
    Relocation
    A relocation rule
    SelectorUtils
    This is a stripped down version of org.codehaus.plexus.util.SelectorUtils for use in Relocation.
